snippet.title: Nick Viall
snippet.description:
Welcome to my podcast The Viall Files!

Celebrity host Nick Viall has found his niche in podcasting. The Viall Files is a weekly multi- episode program that takes a hard look at all types of relationships. On Mondays we connect with our audience as callers “Ask Nick” for advice on all aspects of their lives. On Wednesdays, his one on one interviews with celebrity, pop culture, & expert guests, challenge the way he looks at the world as he dives deep on a variety of topics. Nothing is off limits as Nick gets intimate talking inspiration, friendship, family, dating, & sex with his guests & audience.

Email questions to: asknick@kastmedia.com
